(917, 'NAFLD - PNPLA3 Study', 'In this study 81 non cirrhotic patients are stratified according to PNPLA3 genotypes (27 patients per group, CC,CG,GG). All patients receive a protein shake therapy (HEPAFAST) for 2 weeks and instructions to follow a low glycemic and insulinemic (LOGI) diet for another 6 weeks (EOT). All patients are seen longitudinally for four time points (baseline, week 2, 2 months and 6 months-follow up). At each time point liver fat content is assessed by an independent/blinded investigator with Fibroscan CAP. Additionally Fatty Liver Index (FLI), waist circumference (WC), BMI, HbA1c, triglycerides (TG) and GGT are analyzed.', 'bbmri-eric:ID:AT_MUW:collection:BB9396','collection', 3, 1),
