(1081, 'FFPE blocks Collection', 'We collect and archive FFPE blocks from various neoplasms as well as broad spectrum of non-neoplastic conditions and also normal tissues. Virtually all organ systems are included. The blocks are archived for at least 20 years.', 'bbmri-eric:ID:CZ_CUNI_HK:collection:FFPEblocksCollection','collection', 40, 1),
(1082, 'FFPE slides Collection', 'We archive HE slides from various neoplasms as well as broad spectrum of non-neoplastic conditions and also normal tissues. Virtually all organ systems are included. The slides are archived for at least 5 years.', 'bbmri-eric:ID:CZ_CUNI_HK:collection:FFPEslidesCollection','collection', 40, 1),
(1083, 'Main collection of HK biobank', 'We collect frozen tumor tissue from following neoplasms: breast cancer (C50), colonic cancer (C18-C20), head and neck cancer (in particular; pharyngeal and laryngeal cancer) (C01, C09, C32), borderline tumors of ovary (D39), ovarian cancer (C56), and hepatocellular carcinoma (C22). Paraffin blocks are also available.  Sbíráme nativní vzorky nádorové tkáně u následujících diagnóz: karcinom prsu, kolorektální karcinom, karcinomy oblasti hlavy a krku (zejména karcinomy hltanu a hrtanu), borderline tumory ovaria a karcinomy ovaria, hepatocelulární karcinom. Současně jsou k dispozici parafinové bločky s nádorovou tkání.', 'bbmri-eric:ID:CZ_CUNI_HK:collection:all_samples','collection', 40, 1),
(1084, 'Main collection', 'Main collection comprising all the samples: aliquots of DNA, serum and plasma, subsamples of frozen tissue and tissue in RNALater from particularly pathological tissue (oncology) are stored. It comprises 4,300 retrivals, 2,850 tissue samples, 3,683 blood samples, 534 urine samples, which makes up approximately 80,000 subsamples and aliquots.', 'bbmri-eric:ID:CZ_CUNI_LF1:collection:all_samples','collection', 41, 1),
(1085, 'Existing collection of COVID-19 cases', 'Existing collection of COVID-19 cases', 'bbmri-eric:ID:CZ_CUNI_PILS:collection:COVID19','collection', 42, 1),
