(1087, 'Serum and plasma samples of the Pilsen biobank', 'Biobank at the Department of Immunochemistry Diagnostics, University Hospital Pilsen collects and stores human liquid samples (plasma, serum) and related clinical data of oncological patients.  We focus on long term storage repository. The main diagnoses of interest are: breast cancer, colorectal cancer and prostate cancer. All blood samples are collected at the time of diagnosis prior to the surgery or any other kind of treatment. Two aliquots of serum and two aliquots of plasma samples at the volume of 350 ml are stored at -80°C. Comprehensive clinical data are available through the hospital infromation system.', 'bbmri-eric:ID:CZ_CUNI_PILS:collection:serum_plasma','collection', 42, 1),
(1088, 'Serum and plasma samples with C18-C21 diagnosis', 'Biobank at the Department of Immunochemistry Diagnostics, University Hospital Pilsen collects and stores human liquid samples (plasma, serum) and related clinical data of oncological patients.  We focus on long term storage repository. The main diagnoses of this subcollection is colorectal cancer. All blood samples are collected at the time of diagnosis prior to the surgery or any other kind of treatment. Two aliquots of serum and two aliquots of plasma samples at the volume of 350 ml are stored at -80°C. Comprehensive clinical data are available through the hospital infromation system.', 'bbmri-eric:ID:CZ_CUNI_PILS:collection:serum_plasma:C18-C21','collection', 42, 1),
