(1182, 'Main collection of UPOL biobank', 'We are freezing native samples of cancer tissues and lymph nodes from the pholooing diagnoses: colorectal carcinoma, lung carcinoma, glioma, prostate carcinoma. Material is also processed into FFPE blocks. We archive isolated DNA from colorectal carcinoma, glioma, and melanoms obtained from FFPE blocks and/or plasma. DNA isolation is implemented considering CEN/TS 16835-3,16835-2, 16827-3, but external audit has not been implemented nor the certification was pursued.  Czech version: Zamražujeme nativní vzorky nádorové tkáně a uzlin u následujících diagnóz: kolorektální karcinom, karcinom plic, gliomy, karcinom postaty. Současně jsou k dispozici parafinové bločky s nádorovou tkání. Archivujeme izolovanou DNA kolorektálního karcinomu, karcinomu plic, gliomů a melanomů získanou z FFPE bločků anebo z krevní plazmy. Izolace DNA se provádí s ohledem na normy CEN/TS 16835-3,16835-2, 16827-3, ale externi audit nebyl proveden a o certifikaci nebylo žádáno.', 'bbmri-eric:ID:CZ_UPOL_LF:collection:all_samples','collection', 46, 1),
(1183, 'Isolated DNA collection of UPOL biobank', 'Sub-collection of the UPOL biobanks containing isolated DNA. We archive isolated DNA from colorectal carcinoma, glioma, and melanoms obtained from FFPE blocks and/or plasma. DNA isolation is implemented considering CEN/TS 16835-3,16835-2, 16827-3, but external audit has not been implemented nor the certification was pursued.', 'bbmri-eric:ID:CZ_UPOL_LF:collection:all_samples:DNA','collection', 46, 1),
(1184, 'Cryo-preserved collection of UPOL biobank', 'Sub-collection of the UPOL biobanks containing cryo-preserved biological material and related FFPE blocks. We are freezing native samples of cancer tissues and lymph nodes from the pholooing diagnoses: colorectal carcinoma, lung carcinoma, glioma, prostate carcinoma. Material is also processed into FFPE blocks.', 'bbmri-eric:ID:CZ_UPOL_LF:collection:all_samples:cryo','collection', 46, 1),
